data.text: Aywakni ka an e chuny bur matut, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, yie iwinj dwonda.
Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, ka dine bed ni isiko iparo richo, ma ji timo,
To kata kamano kuomi nitiere weyo richo;
Yaye jo-Israel, keturu genou kuom Jehova Nyasaye, nimar Jehova Nyasaye
En owuon ema obiro waro jo-Israel
